  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13101729/jungfrau-region_switzerland_adobe-stock_117929764_eiger-1.jpg" alt="walking grades" data-udi="umb://media/c945e15e4625481086c6cb9bb2c5b2a1" /></p>
<h2>Boots On Or Off, You Set The Pace</h2>
<p>From gentle strolls to challenging trails, we have walks to suit everyone across our resorts, with each path promising a world of discovery and adventure.</p>
<p>If you've got energy to burn, we've got peaks to conquer and trails to tread. Prefer taking it easy? We've rolled out the green carpet of nature for your serene walks, and fluffed up the pillow for your zen-like spa day. So whether you're seeking the peaks, or unrolling your mat for a spot of yoga, there's an <span style="font-size: 14px;">experience</span> just for you.</p>
<h3>Walk Your Way</h3>
<p>Our Walking Holidays are designed for everyone, but if you're in search of a resort with walks tailored to your pace, we've got you covered. Whether you're seeking a leisurely stroll through nature's wonders or a heart pounding trek that takes you to the summit of adventure you can walk it your way.</p>
<div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our holiday walking grades</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Easy</div>
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13101730/step-further-into-nature-adobestock_320250091.jpg" alt="easy walks" data-udi="umb://media/7389737874974d7ab3c695070f118f12" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">Whether you're new to walking or simply in the mood for a relaxing stroll, these walks are your VIP pass to leisurely exploration.</div>
<div class="c-card__content"></div>
<div class="c-card__content">Ideal for beginners, these resorts offer an effortless introduction to the great outdoors, with well-marked routes that are simple to follow.</div>
<p><strong>Our resort recommendations:</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled, Slovenia</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino, Italy</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne, Switzerland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Challenging</div>
<div class="c-card__img"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093746/challenging-hero.png?width=500&amp;height=261.3793103448276" alt="challenging walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/3ba12c494430493498ec0267c083c192" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>If you love a good leg workout, and have a good head for heights then our resorts with challenging walks are for you.</p>
<p>Expect more mountainous terrain, including steep ascents and descents that demand a solid fitness level and steady footing.</p>
<p><strong>Our resort recommendations:</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix, France</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6}" title="Cinque Terre">Cinque Terre, Italy</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt, Switzerland</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">All Abilities</div>
<div class="c-card__img"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093545/walking.png?width=500&amp;height=280.68965517241384" alt="walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/db390f5eafcc49a382689f02a846aefa" /></span></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Discover resorts perfect for every walking ability.</p>
<p>Whether you're up for a challenge one day and relaxed stroll the next, or if you're unsure about your preferred level, we have you covered.</p>
<p><strong>Our resort recommendations:</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen, Austria</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen">Wengen, Switzerland</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj, Slovenia</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
